canonical:
  title: 議加上尊號箚子
  author: 李詹
  language: lzh
  text: 臣等言伏以殿下卽位之初首念宗廟事重卽以歷代先王先后加上尊號布告中外誠追遠之美意也然追崇大事不可以攝行親祀之則又乖喪三年不祭之義且祭祀當以禮不可以瀆告此臣等之所疑也乞下都評議使典儀寺博考禮文斟酌施行
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 議加上尊號箚子
  author: 李詹
  language: lzh
  text: 臣等言。伏以殿下卽位之初。首念宗廟事重。卽以歷代先王先后。加上尊號。布告中外。誠追遠之美意也。然追崇大事。不可以攝行。親祀之則又乖喪三年不祭之義。且祭祀。當以禮。不可以瀆告。此臣等之所疑也。乞下都評議使典儀寺。博考禮文。斟酌施行。
korean:
  title: 의 가상 존호 차자
  author: 이첨
  language: kor
  text: 신들은 말씀드리옵니다. 전하께서는 즉위하신 당초에 가장 먼저 종묘(宗廟)의 일이 중대함을 생각하시어 역대의 선왕(先王)ㆍ선후(先后)께 존호(尊號)를 가상(加上)하옵시고 이를 서울과 지방에 포고(布告)하셨사오니, 실로 추원(追遠)이 아름다운 뜻이라 여기옵니다. 그러하오나 추숭(追崇)하는 것은 큰 일이 오니 섭행(攝行)하는 것은 불가합니다. 그리고 친사(親祀)하신다해도 또 ‘상(喪)을 당한 3년 동안에는 제사 지내지 않는다’는 뜻에 어긋나오며, 제사는 마땅히 예(禮)로써 하여야지 독고(瀆告)하는 것은 불가하옵니다. 이것을 신들은 해결하지 못하고 있사옵니다. 바라옵기는, 도평의사(都評議使)와 전의시(典儀寺)에 내리시어 예문(禮文)을 널리 상고해서 적절히 시행하도록 하옵소서.
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0590_020_0080&viewSync=OT
english:
  title: Memorial on the Posthumous Elevation of Titles
  author: Lee Cham
  language: eng
  text: Your servant respectfully submits this memorial. When Your Highness ascended the throne, you first turned your attention to the great matter of the ancestral temple. You bestowed posthumous titles upon the ancient kings and queens of former dynasties and proclaimed this throughout the realm—a noble expression of reverence for those who have passed. Yet we are troubled by certain matters of propriety. The elevation of titles is a grave undertaking that cannot be conducted as a provisional act. Should Your Highness perform the sacrifices yourself, this would violate the principle that no offerings are made during the three years of mourning. Furthermore, all sacrifices must be conducted with proper ritual and solemnity—they cannot be undertaken with impropriety. These concerns weigh upon us. We humbly request that this matter be referred to the State Council and the Directorate of Ceremonies, that they may thoroughly examine the ritual texts and determine the appropriate course of action.
  footnotes:
    - The 'three years of mourning' (상삼년불제) refers to the Confucian mourning period during which sacrifices to ancestors are traditionally suspended.
    - The concern about 'provisional conduct' (섭행) reflects worry that improper delegation of ritual duties might diminish their spiritual efficacy.
    - The distinction between proper ritual and irreverent performance (독고) emphasizes the Confucian emphasis on sincere, correct forms in matters of ancestral veneration.
